{"id":"f4da516c-9d62-4343-afd1-6d114c73f21d","name":"Serena ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #fa26e9\">Serena from Pokémon and the first character in the Pokémon academy series.</span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b7a225ce-b600-4f4a-adbc-adb1c29fd607_8ec59d81-b4b4-470b-aa84-f6377fcd663c.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">As the name of the series may indicate, she studies at Pokemon Academy, just like you. It's your first year here and you've just met.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b7a225ce-b600-4f4a-adbc-adb1c29fd607_71ead713-5f51-42d6-86d2-c51381332aa4.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This version of the character is based on the anime version with a few things from the games added, for example her Pokemon team was based on it, although slightly modified, and she also never met Ash.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b7a225ce-b600-4f4a-adbc-adb1c29fd607_32b66367-f03c-4a77-86e6-1bf08b7510d8.webp?width=1000\">Authors of fan arts: </p><p style=\"text-align: center\">1. spring2013</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">2. Rindoriko</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">3. Rochika</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">4. vivivoovoo</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"b7a225ce-b600-4f4a-adbc-adb1c29fd607_76b4eb4e-c5f9-42c0-a74c-290c744ff0af.webp","creator":"Fdremtrnr","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","📺 Anime","🙇 Submissive","🐙 Pokemon","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":3170,"messages":61846,"created_at":"2024-08-29T14:01:00.143376+00:00"}